00083 void BusIfGeneralDetails::restoreChanges() {
00084 
00085         connRequired_.setChecked(busif_->getConnectionRequired());
00086         bitsInLau_.setValue(busif_->getBitsInLau());
00087         int endiannessIndex = endianness_.findText(
00088                 General::endianness2Str(busif_->getEndianness()));
00089         endianness_.setCurrentIndex(endiannessIndex);
00090 
00091         // if bit steering is not specified
00092         if (busif_->getBitSteering() == General::BITSTEERING_UNSPECIFIED) {
00093                 bitSteering_.setDisabled(true);
00094                 bitSteering_.setCurrentIndex(-1);
00095                 bitSteeringEnabled_.setChecked(false);
00096         }
00097         // if bitsteering is specified then set it to correct value
00098         else {
00099                 bitSteeringEnabled_.setChecked(true);
00100                 bitSteering_.setEnabled(true);
00101                 int bitSteeringIndex = bitSteering_.findText(
00102                         General::bitSteering2Str(busif_->getBitSteering()));
00103                 bitSteering_.setCurrentIndex(bitSteeringIndex);
00104         }
00105 
00106 }

00108 void BusIfGeneralDetails::applyChanges() {
00109 
00110         busif_->setConnectionRequired(connRequired_.isChecked());
00111         busif_->setBitsInLau(bitsInLau_.value());
00112         busif_->setEndianness(General::str2Endianness(endianness_.currentText(),
00113                 General::LITTLE));
00114 
00115         // if bit steering is enabled
00116         if (bitSteeringEnabled_.isChecked()) {
00117                 busif_->setBitSteering(General::str2BitSteering(bitSteering_.currentText()));
00118         }
00119         // if it was disabled
00120         else {
00121                 busif_->setBitSteering(General::BITSTEERING_UNSPECIFIED);
00122         }
00123 }
